    "title": "Opening for Software Engineer at iCliniq",
    "description": "iCliniq invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Software Engineer at our Ranchi location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout iCliniq:\niCliniq is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with iCliniq!",
